{
  "version": "1.2.0",
  "releaseNotes": {
    "zh": [
      "新增 EPUB 与可编辑 DOCX 导出，并在应用内提供与 PDF 一致的阅读、缩放和分享体验。",
      "修复 macOS 更新后历史记录消失的问题，并为生成记录增加独立持久化备份。",
      "桌面端侧边栏新增平滑自动收窄与手动展开按钮，首次使用界面不再出现错误侧栏。",
      "生成完成后可关闭进度卡片；修复 Android 长时间闲置或后台恢复后偶发卡死。"
    ],
    "en": [
      "Added EPUB and editable DOCX export with in-app reading, zooming, and sharing consistent with PDF.",
      "Fixed missing macOS history after updates and added a durable local history backup.",
      "Added a smoothly adaptive desktop sidebar with a manual compact toggle and fixed the first-run sidebar artifact.",
      "Added dismissible completed progress and fixed rare Android freezes after long idle or background resume."
    ]
  },
